column1: Who is John Doe?;John Doe is a placeholder name used as a pseudonym in legal cases
column2: when the true identity of the person is unknown or protected. It is also commonly used to refer to a hypothetical

column1: What is jenkins?;Jenkins is an open source automation server. It is used to automate all sorts of tasks such as building
column3: and deploying software. It is a popular tool in the software development community and is used by companies large and small. Jenkins can be used to easily set up continuous integration and continuous delivery (CI/CD) pipelines

column1: What is jenkins?;Jenkins is an open source automation server that is used to automate software development. It assists in automating the non-human part of the software development process
column2: with continuous integration and facilitating technical aspects of the continuous delivery process. Jenkins manages and controls the development process by setting up jobs
